ernational_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-415-28038-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-415-28038-9\">0-415-28038-9</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">17 June</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Meeting+the+needs+of+children+with+disabilities%3A+families+and+professionals+facing+the+challenge+together&amp;rft.place=Chapter+2&amp;rft.pub=Routledge&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.isbn=0-415-28038-9&amp;rft.au=Helen+Warner&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fhl%3Den%26lr%3D%26id%3D1-CvZFkPk9IC%26oi%3Dfnd%26pg%3DPA14%26dq%3D%2522Silent%2BMinority%2522%2Bdocumentary%2B1981%2Bbritish%2Btelevision%26ots%3DoswZEXVDLT%26sig%3DLLBi-T6BDbX1Zu6TKhfctHysNUo&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASilent+Minority\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Tizard_Learning_Disability_Review-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Tizard_Learning_Disability_Review_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Murphy, G. (2000). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://direct.bl.uk/bld/PlaceOrder.do?UIN=077869876&amp;ETOC=RN&amp;from=searchengine\">\"Policy and Service Development Trends: Forensic Mental Health and Social Care Services\"</a>. <i>Tizard Learning Disability Review</i>. Pavilion. <b>5</b> (Part 2): 32\u201335. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1108/13595474200000016\">10.1108/13595474200000016</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.world